          "Khaldoun Khelil"
        ],
        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "A Tremere Antitribu who survived the death of the rest of his clan. He is a student of darker Thaumaturgy and is often tempted to infernalism. While the rest of his blood line died he was likely spared because he was at the Sabbat Regents side and protected by multiple layers of magical warding.  Dabir was a Regent in Baghdad, but defected to House Goratrix when he was revealed as a member of the Horned Society.  In the Sabbat he quickly realized that many in House Goratrix were infernalists and if not for the Black Hands intervention may have joined their number.  After the fall of his Clan and the reorganization of the Black Hand, Dabir still finds himself tempted by the power of infernalism, but cannot abide the idea of a demonic master.  He is in LA invetigating the rumor that new gargoyles are being created and how the Sabbat can counter these creatures... but he also wishes to learn more about LA's demons and how they can be captured or destroyed."
        ],
